{"tid":1626523,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[行動POST]10月6港島和平遊行","createTime":"2019-10-05T11:37:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T06:10:58.000Z","uid":261478,"like":78,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"3a8d94ebf0cc86db64f77e857f30e9f56b8a50ff","tid":1626523,"uid":261478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:37:54.000Z","msg":"聽曰港島記住係和平遊行<br />\n盡量吸多D和理非出黎<br />\n和理非唔好怕無不反對通知書<br />\n香港已經唔講法律<br />\n有不反對通知書都照拉鳩你架啦<br />\n所以聽日為香港全世界出黎港島<br />\n勇和一家目標300萬人和平遊行<br />\n畀人知道香港人係和平嘅<br />\n暴力嘅係政府<br />\n要吸多D國際支持<br />\n<br />\n同時我唔反對衝衝子去衝<br />\n但記住要散水返左屋企先<br />\n避免畀狗圍無路走唔到<br />\n返左屋企之後再係屋企步行範圍內快閃游擊<br />\n拆鐵拆政府建築幫中資國企裝修<br />\n裝修到星期二開唔到門就變相三罷<br />\n唔好等有狗出現就要散水轉場<br />\n記住我地優勢係人多機動性高<br />\n攰同餓就返屋企食飯休息回滿升先再第日出過<br />\n有唔對路就返屋企訓覺唔好送頭"},{"pid":"ffeac8f89edd17f0a3f9f409fd70062942cbff3a","tid":1626523,"uid":274686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:38:33.000Z","msg":"推！！！！！！！"},{"pid":"610f0a5ad263c9862a3924afde828b36d3a6f68c","tid":1626523,"uid":261478,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:39:11.000Z","msg":"認同就推POST<br />\n同用其他方法spread開去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"372df17598679e833a8e14dc7be9743374424fe4","tid":1626523,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:52:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f79263a25fc6cc5919a1292be71771327efbc86","tid":1626523,"uid":119720,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:52:46.000Z","msg":"推！！和理非回合<br />\n<br />\n香港人能和能勇 收放自如"},{"pid":"c53f76c8ed4550eddc876c93fd3f01ab3e6fdd09","tid":1626523,"uid":312883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:55:53.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c0c8fa3b1b1175197745c36d28855d002ac1e91e","tid":1626523,"uid":19057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:57:35.000Z","msg":"